<center><a href="https://higherme.com/locations/57e531f5d0936?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=l%3A1340%3Askokie%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-thursday" rel="nofollow">
<img border="0" alt="HigherMe_Apply" src="http://i60.tinypic.com/15qd6ja.png" width="300" height="66"></a></center>

<br> <font size="5"><b>CPK is now hiring BOH and FOH positions in Skokie!</b></font>
 <br> <h2></h2> <h3>Who Are We?</h3> <font size="4">This is the place for TASTE makers, RULE breakers and EARTH shakers who conquer challenges by daring to work on the edge and thinking outside the box. We call ourselves the EPIC Nation because we are all working toward a common goal around the world, and we have the most amazing time doing it. We bring the BIGGEST and BEST parts of ourselves to work and to our communities, and that simple idea just makes us better as a whole. Our philosophy is when you have a passion for something, there's no stopping you. So at CPK, go ahead. Be Bold. Be You. Be EPIC. We are the EPIC Nation.

Who doesn't like contests on the regular where the prizes are Ipads, free food, gift cards, X-Boxes, etc.? Also, where else does your team and your regulars consider you to be as close as family? We know, we're pretty awesome. Check us out and apply today!
</font> <br> <br>


 <h3>Who Are We Looking For?</h3> <font size="4">

We are looking for bright and energetic people to join our team. We are looking for passionate individuals with hospitality in their blood. We have a full training program that won't leave you hanging, long time employees who love their job and meeting new people, free food for performance, daily meal discounts, gift cards, weekly contests, cash prizes, etc. What more could you ask for in the #bestjobevercpk?  

Currently we are hiring for many roles, including:
<br><strong>
<ul><li>Bartender</li>
<li>Bussers</li>
<li>Cook</li>
<li>Dishwasher</li>
<li>Host/Hostess</li>
<li>Servers</li></ul></strong>


We are looking for passionate individuals with hospitality in their blood. We have a full training program that won't leave you hanging, long time employees who love their job and meeting new people, free food for performance, daily meal discounts, gift cards, weekly contests, cash prizes, etc. What more could you ask for in the #bestjobevercpk? 
<br><br>
California Pizza Kitchen is an Equal Opportunity Employer.
<br><br>
